{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there was always, every night, there was like terrible cries, and yelling, and moaning, and-- and-- and you could really see the fire.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I wasn't big enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I was lucky that they didn't pick me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Real tired, yeah, and I was really received some severe beating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was beaten with a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--whip on my rear, but that was already-- that was easy, that was easier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was beaten up pretty badly, which also took me a while to get over it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, but in-- but in Funfteichen, I was beaten a different way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was hit with a shovel, and I was hit with the-- with the--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with the elbows in my face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hersbruck.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, and that was-- I was lucky that this was the rear end, because in Hersbruck, they had different kind of methods which I haven't seen in other camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would-- they would take you into the-- the kapos-- they would send the kapos with you to take you to the bathroom, and they would turn on the hose and stick it in your inside and turn it on, so that you, the body, would explode.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, in through-- into your mouth and down the-- your trachea.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one ever survived that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was, right, because I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got up real quick, and I got dressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- they thought maybe-- and I was also younger-- so they thought maybe I will do some work for a little bit longer, you know, because youth had a lot to do with being alive.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, a potluck had also a lot to do with it, because you never knew when you will get hit or with what.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
